text: Prince Antasari, also known by his Indonesian name Pangeran Antasari, was a sultan of Banjar . Antasari was born in 1797. He was son of Prince Mashud and grandson of Prince Amir. He was a prince from a line of the royal family whose power had been usurped in the 18th century. Category:1797 births Category:1862 deaths Category:Indonesian people
title: Prince Antasari
